### Option 2: AWS Cognito + IAM Roles
- Temporary credentials with limited permissions
- No credentials in code
- Takes 15-20 minutes

### Option 3: Backend Proxy
- Simple Node.js/Python server handles AWS/Google calls
- Deploy on Heroku/Vercel (free tier)
- Takes 20-30 minutes

### Option 4: Firebase Storage + Cloud Functions
- No AWS needed
- Credentials managed by Firebase
- Takes 15 minutes

